From 9a8f7c3b2e1d4f5a6b8c9d0e1f2a3b4c5d6e7f80 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: 10BE Software UG <support@ns.10be.de>
Date: Mon, 1 Jun 2026 14:00:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Allow 10BE CarbCam to open the Bolus Wizard with prefilled
 carbs

Adds a whitelisted external entry point that lets 10BE CarbCam
(package de.be10.carbcam) open the standard AAPS Bolus Wizard with
the carbs field prefilled.

Design notes:

  * Caller package is verified against a hard-coded whitelist in
    WizardLaunchActivity. Any other caller is silently rejected.
  * Carbs are bounds-checked to 1..80 g; out-of-range values are
    silently rejected. Larger meals can be adjusted manually in the
    wizard afterwards.
  * The launcher activity only forwards the value to MainActivity,
    which then opens the unmodified WizardDialog with the carbs
    field prefilled. All AAPS confirmation dialogs, safety checks and
    bolus logic remain unchanged.
  * No insulin is ever delivered without the standard confirmation
    flow.

Intent contract:

  action  : info.nightscout.androidaps.action.OPEN_BOLUS_WIZARD
  extras  : carbs  (int,    required, 1..80, grams)
            notes  (string, optional)
            source (string, optional, free-form caller tag)

Target branch: AAPS master 3.4.2.2
